= Introduction ============================
Here is the files and scripts to run simulation and analysis results
It can work as standalone, but also test with other subsystems and full SoLID simulation

=run ec simulation standalone==============

#in graphic
solid_gemc solid_PVDIS_LD2_ec_segmented.gcard -EXEC_MACRO="../../../solid_gemc2/script/solid_slice.vis" -geometry="1000x1000" -HIGH_RES="1" 
solid_gemc solid_SIDIS_He3_ec_segmented.gcard -EXEC_MACRO="../../../solid_gemc2/script/solid_slice.vis" -geometry="1000x1000" -HIGH_RES="1" 

#in batch
solid_gemc solid_PVDIS_LD2_ec_segmented.gcard -BEAM_P="e-,5*GeV,25*deg,0*deg" -SPREAD_P="0*GeV,0*deg,0*deg" -BEAM_V="(0,0,10)cm" -N=1e3 -OUTPUT="evio,output.evio" -PRINT_EVENT=1 -USE_GUI=0
solid_gemc solid_SIDIS_He3_ec_segmented.gcard   -BEAM_P="e-,5*GeV,12*deg,0*deg" -SPREAD_P="0*GeV,0*deg,0*deg" -BEAM_V="(0,0,-350)cm" -N=1e3 -OUTPUT="evio,output.evio" -PRINT_EVENT=1 -USE_GUI=0

#convert evio file in standalone simulation to root file
evio2root -INPUTF=output.evio -B="../ec_solid_gemc/solid_PVDIS_ec_forwardangle"
evio2root -INPUTF=output.evio -B="../ec_solid_gemc/solid_SIDIS_ec_forwardangle ../ec_solid_gemc/solid_SIDIS_ec_largeangle"

== run ec simulation with other subsystems =====
same commands as in standalone mode, just replace the gcards with these two 
solid_PVDIS_LD2_full.gcard
solid_SIDIS_He3_full.gcard

#convert evio file in full simulation to root file
evio2root -INPUTF=output.evio -B="../ec_solid_gemc/solid_PVDIS_ec_forwardangle ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/lgc/solid_PVDIS_lgc ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/gem/solid_PVDIS_gem"
evio2root -INPUTF=output.evio -B="../ec_solid_gemc/solid_SIDIS_ec_forwardangle ../ec_solid_gemc/solid_SIDIS_ec_largeangle ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/hgc/solid_SIDIS_hgc ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/lgc/solid_SIDIS_lgc ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/hgc/solid_SIDIS_hgc ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/gem/solid_SIDIS_gem ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/mrpc/solid_SIDIS_mrpc_forwardangle ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/spd/solid_SIDIS_spd_forwardangle ../../../solid_gemc2/geometry/spd/solid_SIDIS_spd_largeangle"

== analysis ============================
the general script analysis.C calls the ec script analysis_tree_solid_ec.C
run it as compiled script in root as follows
root> .x analysis.C+("output.root")

== how to obain energy resolution ===========

run standalone simulation with a fixed electron energy
analysis the result by using analysis.C
A energy deposition distribution plot will show up, record the mean and sigma
run various electron energies, then analysis and record all mean and signa
Put mean and sigma into resolution.C
run resolution.C to plot and fit the energy resolution




